A simple rule transition demo, using AS3 and Android.


!!!!!NOTE:!!!!!

AvoidXfermode is deprecated since API 16, please use gles 2.0 or other methods.

!!!!!NOTE:!!!!!


NOTE:
1. as3/ & android/ : Demo sources.
2. c/ : Rule images generater (only for test).
3. For rule images, You can use translib2.lzh instead. (See http://kikyou.info/tvp/) 
4. Rule images should be .png format, for lossless compression.

